S.FORM: minamilingan aicu "aljak na mazazangiljan a ti paisi ", mavan a milimilingan nua sedjerman i iyurupu (Europe) tua tja kakedriyan. a i sangasangasan a vinecikan aicu a milimilingan i tua sinansunatj nua madrusa a kaka a lja grimm (The Brothers Grimm) a minamilingan nua lja grimm (Grimms' Fairy Tales) ka 1812 a caviljan. sinanljavaran aicu a "Sneewittchen" nua i kakaian a djermany. minamilingan sinanzugan ni velanz (Franz Jüttner) tua aljak na mazazangiljan a ti paisi (1905)

minamilingan aico "aljak na mazazangiljan a ti paisi ", mavan a milimilingan noa sedjerman i iyoropo (Eorope) toa tja kakedriyan. a i sangasangasan a vinecikan aico a milimilingan i toa sinansonatj noa madrosa a kaka a lja grimm (The Brothers Grimm) a minamilingan noa lja grimm (Grimms' Fairy Tales) ka 1812 a caviljan. sinanljavaran aico a "Sneewittchen" noa i kakaian a djermany. minamilingan sinanzogan ni velanz (Franz Jüttner) toa aljak na mazazangiljan a ti paisi (1905)
